## ðŸ”¹ Code Blocks

### Inline Code
Use backticks for `single commands` like this.

### Multi-line Code Block
Use three backticks (```) followed by the language name (bash, python, html) for syntax highlighting:

```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade -y
